Module org.example.proyecto
Package org.example.proyecto.model.account

Class AccountDTO

java.lang.Object
org.example.proyecto.model.account.AccountDTO
Direct Known Subclasses:
ClientDTO, UserDTO
public class AccountDTO extends Object
Data Transfer Object (DTO) for account information. This class encapsulates the data of an account and provides methods for accessing and manipulating this data.

2024-05-28
